{"title":"Anemia Hemolítica Autoinmune","guid":"","filepath":"/Users/criaah/Vault/📚 Resources/Mapas-Mentales/Entidades clínicas/Hematología/Anemia Hemolítica Autoinmune-2024.smmx","root":{"id":"0","parent":"-1","text":"Anemia Hemolítica\\NAutoinmune","guid":"O_N7FXaBpZ_lnj-O34-QOw","children":[{"id":"1","parent":"0","text":"Caso\\Nclínico","guid":"71uUE9TEjiKXAeC3yPCVRg","children":[{"id":"2","parent":"1","text":"Información\\Ndel Paciente:","guid":"IGYx4AFHz9uDDFyGiz8ZIg","children":[{"id":"3","parent":"2","text":"Mujer, 28 años.","guid":"XCKiQtFb9xtq52zFCgyj2A","children":[]},{"id":"4","parent":"2","text":"Sin antecedentes mórbidos de relevancia.","guid":"2qbZl5EcO6Q0OZcYEkKqNA","children":[]}]},{"id":"5","parent":"1","text":"Motivo de\\NConsulta:","guid":"edi0cjttoWhVZojPxng0AA","children":[{"id":"6","parent":"5","text":"Cuadro de 2 semanas de evolución de palidez, astenia y\\Ndisnea progresiva hasta hacerse de mínimos esfuerzos.","guid":"Owng4CEXuAaqUkfW1zGn1g","children":[]}]},{"id":"7","parent":"1","text":"Examen Físico:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"8","parent":"7","text":"PA: 110/70 mmHg. FC: 105 lpm. T°: 37.2°C.","guid":"8SrpUKWRt0SYkCrcXyfgwQ","children":[]},{"id":"9","parent":"7","text":"Palidez de piel y mucosas.","guid":"6yFSiORJW_fmUbbOyp37rw","children":[]},{"id":"10","parent":"7","text":"Ictericia conjuntival.","guid":"hyt_YwRqabJf6U-hlk6MWQ","children":[]},{"id":"11","parent":"7","text":"Esplenomegalia 3 cm bajo reborde costal izquierdo.","guid":"wREA-6Ha2sTvZcM2gXuwdw","children":[]},{"id":"12","parent":"7","text":"Sin adenopatías.","guid":"oEx4fSV4iM-DYnwp3J52Fg","children":[]},{"id":"13","parent":"7","text":"Resto del examen sin hallazgos patológicos.","guid":"lsblg7_1VPBLx2ixf28msw","children":[]}]},{"id":"14","parent":"1","text":"Laboratorio:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"15","parent":"14","text":"Reticulocitos: 12% (VN: 0.5-2.5)","guid":"NWk8Nha8QUPgAdyOTcOboA","children":[]},{"id":"16","parent":"14","text":"Hemoglobina: 6.2 g/dL (VN: 12-16)","guid":"EU4IA4rirhFXfh3JfxN7UA","children":[]},{"id":"17","parent":"14","text":"VCM: 89 fL (VN: 80-100)","guid":"ATSRiABo8xWktRoBQI0qKg","children":[]},{"id":"18","parent":"14","text":"CHCM: 35 g/dL (VN: 32-36)","guid":"7t79kDqMAx_z8t1F16D9Nw","children":[]},{"id":"19","parent":"14","text":"Leucocitos: 8,500/uL (VN: 4,000-10,000)","guid":"9HoZpMp96hTUHkRdzL0pfA","children":[]},{"id":"20","parent":"14","text":"Plaquetas: 350,000/uL (VN: 150,000-400,000)","guid":"5Mk8KvIz1OCT8MTWZdwAJw","children":[]},{"id":"21","parent":"14","text":"LDH: 980 U/L (VN: 120-246)","guid":"6V2M00-ZnQBgiXVSzfqLYw","children":[]},{"id":"22","parent":"14","text":"Bilirrubina Total: 4.2 mg/dL (VN: 0.3-1. 2), Directa: 0.6, Indirecta: 3.6","guid":"QYGRPdwyp4a2tnqRSEHxMw","children":[]},{"id":"23","parent":"14","text":"Haptoglobina: 10 mg/dL (VN: 30-200)","guid":"kKY6mqDFcySHhMQSmpdAyA","children":[]},{"id":"24","parent":"14","text":"Frotis Sanguíneo:","guid":"zvtuxZGU_FVWmQJcJKfi4A","children":[{"id":"25","parent":"24","text":"Anisocitosis y policromasia marcada. Abundantes esferocitos.","guid":"TIPVOVElvgQtju4MJ5GyPg","children":[]}]},{"id":"26","parent":"14","text":"Coombs Directo:","guid":"VTMXQWNNKwStuYGTigFd8Q","children":[{"id":"27","parent":"26","text":"Positivo ++, IgG +++, C3d +","guid":"e9ygI6iyQctCZKABChYPFQ","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"28","parent":"1","text":"Diagnóstico:","guid":"QBp8IeQDvChdl9me6TWlGA","children":[{"id":"29","parent":"28","text":"Anemia Hemolítica Autoinmune por\\NAnticuerpos Calientes primaria.","guid":"28vrA3nRh6PrDL6eBsA2ag","children":[]}]},{"id":"30","parent":"1","text":"Manejo:","guid":"i_O3qpGShOyUKyqmXO7ftg","children":[{"id":"31","parent":"30","text":"Transfusión de 2 unidades de GR compatibilizados.","guid":"2HSPDZxsERdYF4GmilQbsA","children":[]},{"id":"32","parent":"30","text":"Metilprednisolona 1 mg/kg/día vía oral.","guid":"j2u1Pfdm2dVsdwKDhfgR1w","children":[]},{"id":"33","parent":"30","text":"Ácido fólico 5 mg/día vía oral.","guid":"08LVC9OBKRJUHF_dT_nGaQ","children":[]},{"id":"34","parent":"30","text":"Control ambulatorio en 1 semana con nuevo hemograma y perfil de hemólisis.","guid":"UGvW9iUmnglAZvmMQ5GY9Q","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"35","parent":"0","text":"Perlas","guid":"bOR60pDZI7LGTVc15htrIg","children":[{"id":"36","parent":"35","text":"- ¿Qué es la anemia hemolítica autoinmune?","guid":"ssWF9fVioeDxlRJMUt0wiw","children":[{"id":"37","parent":"36","text":"Es un trastorno autoinmune que resulta en la destrucción de glóbulos rojos mediada por autoanticuerpos. (1)","guid":"a8ssL70z57Vh2SqtEdd6Aw","children":[]}]},{"id":"38","parent":"35","text":"- ¿Cuáles son los principales subtipos serológicos de AHAI?","guid":"bULOono7ty2M_FqQF-o8zQ","children":[{"id":"39","parent":"38","text":"AHAI por anticuerpos calientes (IgG), AHAI por anticuerpos fríos (IgM) y AHAI mixta. (2)","guid":"GA4nvjco_S2wspLAbDy4Pg","children":[]}]},{"id":"40","parent":"35","text":"- ¿Cuál es el principal objetivo terapéutico en AHAI?","guid":"9NsBgRIY1a24UeVZVjyBww","children":[{"id":"41","parent":"40","text":"Disminuir la destrucción de glóbulos rojos y la producción de autoanticuerpos. (3)","guid":"-rz08-zuOe48qgK84XD0bQ","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"42","parent":"0","text":"Definición","guid":"","children":[{"id":"43","parent":"42","text":"- La anemia hemolítica autoinmune (AHAI) es un trastorno hemolítico adquirido, mediado por autoanticuerpos\\Ndirigidos contra antígenos de superficie de los eritrocitos, que lleva a su destrucción prematura. (1)","guid":"cvadIOyAOC2c9h-mlc6b0Q","children":[]},{"id":"44","parent":"42","text":"- Primeras descripciones en 1940s, posterior al desarrollo del test de Coombs. (4)","guid":"4fPfyDU-fC6BbHwoWihkkA","children":[]}]},{"id":"45","parent":"0","text":"Fisiopatología","guid":"","children":[{"id":"46","parent":"45","text":"- Autoanticuerpos (IgG, IgM) reconocen antígenos en superficie de eritrocitos. (1)","guid":"zj3G6ELZZ2NIpMp2R3v6xg","children":[]},{"id":"47","parent":"45","text":"- IgG lleva a fagocitosis extravascular principalmente en bazo.\\NIgM activa complemento y lleva a hemólisis intravascular. (5)","guid":"6ZhYDuSmWUEBsilvAanfRg","children":[]},{"id":"48","parent":"45","text":"- Activación de macrófagos vía receptor Fc. Citotoxicidad celular dependiente de anticuerpos (ADCC). (1)","guid":"dUw850GpYhxk2cgc5KyAxw","children":[]},{"id":"49","parent":"45","text":"- Disregulación de células T y B autorreactivas. (6)","guid":"219nMBvAFsrk3dQjyH89Ug","children":[]},{"id":"50","parent":"45","text":"- Objetivos\\Nterapéuticos","guid":"tthJ1a4oSmztDGm79DZdvQ","children":[{"id":"51","parent":"50","text":"Inmunosupresión, depleción de células B (rituximab),\\Ninhibidores del complemento (sutimlimab). (3)","guid":"TxLo0bPGbuxe6Fb2s70FYA","children":[]}]},{"id":"52","parent":"45","text":"- Preguntas abiertas","guid":"ycUhsb0Mu5ewP0cMTc2Lbw","children":[{"id":"53","parent":"52","text":"Rol de coestimulación/checkpoint y vías JAK en patogénesis. (6)","guid":"yE0TediYFUH6dl5aXPqCDw","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"54","parent":"0","text":"Epidemiología","guid":"","children":[{"id":"55","parent":"54","text":"- Incidencia","guid":"lgoOoTZNrW_td-oQFF3nRg","children":[{"id":"56","parent":"55","text":"0.8-3 casos por 100,000 personas-año. (7)","guid":"Xy5JfThNQR0CP38Y8d-INw","children":[]}]},{"id":"57","parent":"54","text":"- Prevalencia","guid":"809B-YMCu6N1tEHa9ccLRQ","children":[{"id":"58","parent":"57","text":"17 por 100,000. Pico entre 60-70 años. (7)","guid":"NSwK-NwpFfQpN2Z1dCw9Dw","children":[]}]},{"id":"59","parent":"54","text":"- Discapacidad y necesidad transfusional en >50% de casos. Mortalidad 20% a 3 años. (8)","guid":"mtYyxMTwRyJ1QSTuPoG45A","children":[]},{"id":"60","parent":"54","text":"- En Chile","guid":"_tNYfCLoDv8yJ52klzo6ZQ","children":[{"id":"61","parent":"60","text":"No hay datos poblacionales. Series pequeñas de centros de referencia. (9)","guid":"p_-hZhRkuotIPH3Jg81-Vg","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"62","parent":"0","text":"Factores de riesgo","guid":"","children":[{"id":"63","parent":"62","text":"- Edad avanzada (>60 años). RR: 4.1  (10)","guid":"1IF8dKXhXtdG9cKcCxD6pg","children":[]},{"id":"64","parent":"62","text":"- Sexo femenino. RR: 2.1 (10)","guid":"uh7z7gyx3BiL8zFfQCuHJw","children":[]},{"id":"65","parent":"62","text":"- Antecedente de otra enfermedad autoinmune. RR: 8.9 (10)","guid":"lDJaUI2ej3-am3hW_exCMA","children":[]},{"id":"66","parent":"62","text":"- Infecciones virales (VEB, VIH, VHC). RR: 3.2 (10)","guid":"XCrW6so9pTSKDIie_DIzTw","children":[]},{"id":"67","parent":"62","text":"- Neoplasias linfoides. RR: 5.8 (10)","guid":"oJsZ19nnS0eDYycf-ko2kg","children":[]}]},{"id":"68","parent":"0","text":"Causas","guid":"","children":[{"id":"69","parent":"68","text":"- Idiopática (~50%)","guid":"oVsHc1IvObRHWwFdyGvu9w","children":[]},{"id":"70","parent":"68","text":"- Enf. linfoproliferativas (20-30%)","guid":"coTinNMSt-bPUmK2tCB95w","children":[{"id":"71","parent":"70","text":"LLC, linfoma, macroglobulinemia.","guid":"SujajUCzSzyKuxPJ1bwlSg","children":[]}]},{"id":"72","parent":"68","text":"- Enf. autoinmunes (20-30%)","guid":"gCpoeEaxiUG-QvpxAkm_gQ","children":[{"id":"73","parent":"72","text":"LES, AR, síndrome antifosfolípidos.","guid":"3-p-BYpSXHrGa2PvQAc_wQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"74","parent":"68","text":"- Infecciones virales (5-10%)","guid":"4Erh8h9NlgwgBW1fwba-Hw","children":[{"id":"75","parent":"74","text":"VEB, VHC, VIH, influenza, neumonía por micoplasma.","guid":"OkuGdnQWJTr1L02eWzLgWA","children":[]}]},{"id":"76","parent":"68","text":"- Drogas/toxinas (<5%)","guid":"SSoP-Z_PR0VQYKHKsV3AZw","children":[{"id":"77","parent":"76","text":"α-metildopa, penicilinas, quinidina, cefalosporinas. (1,3,4)","guid":"10IgoNRStx6Q1ubK4e0GLQ","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"78","parent":"0","text":"Clínica","guid":"","children":[{"id":"79","parent":"78","text":"- Anemia de inicio agudo o subagudo.","guid":"Xmw30RTnR1hqUj0AB8bFDg","children":[]},{"id":"80","parent":"78","text":"- Palidez, fatiga, taquicardia, disnea de esfuerzos.","guid":"Dpx1lpPHQvVwtXQjRUVESg","children":[]},{"id":"81","parent":"78","text":"- Ictericia, esplenomegalia en examen físico (50-60%).","guid":"dhFua6o33y_cCXAsHSA0wQ","children":[]},{"id":"82","parent":"78","text":"- Triada clínica","guid":"atWc466G1i-UUDBrr53loQ","children":[{"id":"83","parent":"82","text":"Anemia + reticulocitosis + hiperbilirrubinemia indirecta.","guid":"rGUTdGTGlUd4UNQGxbEgOQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"84","parent":"78","text":"- Hemoglobinuria en casos de hemólisis intravascular.","guid":"-_wJAymJLSPxcMp7iA906Q","children":[]},{"id":"85","parent":"78","text":"- Livedo reticularis, acrocianosis en AHAI por anticuerpos fríos.","guid":"k1pna5dDkDAe94dHk67yyg","children":[]},{"id":"86","parent":"78","text":"- Factores de\\Nmal pronóstico","guid":"t76ny_cr3ePNezXCer8gpg","children":[{"id":"87","parent":"86","text":"Hb <6 g/dL, reticulocitopenia (respuesta medular inefectiva),\\Nhemólisis intravascular. (3)","guid":"_qhoJTQn-ywKUKIPoOVaBg","children":[]}]},{"id":"88","parent":"78","text":"- Complicaciones","guid":"cJW4JnWqwzGLvdePMpj7tQ","children":[{"id":"89","parent":"88","text":"Anemia severa con falla cardiaca, trombosis venosa (25-30%), infecciones. (8)","guid":"8VW7G9Hp5Sp3eE0oJCxrYg","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"90","parent":"0","text":"Estudio","guid":"","children":[{"id":"91","parent":"90","text":"- Hemograma","guid":"IoK7IdItTZrnQiYYbCeAqA","children":[{"id":"92","parent":"91","text":"Anemia normocítica (Hb <12 g/dL en mujeres, <13 g/dL en hombres),\\Nreticulocitosis. VCM normal, CHCM aumentado. LDH aumentada.","guid":"AoAzEQSXDGsB8gVuk719rA","children":[]}]},{"id":"93","parent":"90","text":"- Frotis","guid":"qGYlZPW7ifBUIorMug6CzA","children":[{"id":"94","parent":"93","text":"Esferocitos, policromasia.","guid":"RtNZwoasIwpjgtbB_7v9nw","children":[]}]},{"id":"95","parent":"90","text":"- Hiperbilirrubinemia de predominio indirecta (>1.2 mg/dL).","guid":"w-RESq6WgUr678DskQfRBQ","children":[]},{"id":"96","parent":"90","text":"Prueba de Coombs\\NDirecto (PCD):","guid":"Asyg5R9haMRpDSxvVbdlVA","children":[{"id":"97","parent":"96","text":"Detecta anticuerpos unidos a la superficie de los eritrocitos.","guid":"Ksjy7jLL19Zo-gi_csgJiw","children":[]},{"id":"98","parent":"96","text":"Positiva en >95% de los casos de AHAI por anticuerpos calientes. (1)","guid":"ea_r62w51Q9cfel-X-i_YA","children":[]},{"id":"99","parent":"96","text":"Permite clasificar según\\Npatrón de positividad:","guid":"fFZ6ZCbwh-lpMQula5vByQ","children":[{"id":"100","parent":"99","text":"IgG +/- C3d: AHAI por Ac calientes.","guid":"FdiHYz-H_GtOJae5VFFJhQ","children":[]},{"id":"101","parent":"99","text":"C3d aislado: AHAI por Ac fríos.","guid":"b-T7nCLvOGMhESu1KLqcfg","children":[]},{"id":"102","parent":"99","text":"IgG + C3d: AHAI mixta.","guid":"dFFo7g2MGjUpIJ9NZntR7w","children":[]}]},{"id":"103","parent":"96","text":"Fundamental para el diagnóstico. Especificidad 98% para AHAI. (2)","guid":"UeTqW1VLv21iJ8KkRVUZvw","children":[]}]},{"id":"104","parent":"90","text":"Según sospecha","guid":"SpnGxC8ls3SrMzxLpg8rnw","children":[{"id":"105","parent":"104","text":"Prueba de Coombs\\NIndirecto (PCI):","guid":"UdbKwQ5dyE9kEKC4CxHLQA","children":[{"id":"106","parent":"105","text":"Detecta anticuerpos libres en suero contra antígenos eritrocitarios.","guid":"Wos0A0cT_I8NM3zcBVQm8g","children":[]},{"id":"107","parent":"105","text":"Positiva en 30-40% de los casos de AHAI por Ac calientes. (3)","guid":"ed_UZXYthZx4HDB9c4_AUA","children":[]},{"id":"108","parent":"105","text":"Permite identificar especificidad\\Nde aloanticuerpos:","guid":"Ymdaq1SaGftTeH-wXr3VDw","children":[{"id":"109","parent":"108","text":"Útil para búsqueda de unidades compatibles para transfusión.","guid":"e4qh5Dypi1VKWZbZEWMpRw","children":[]},{"id":"110","parent":"108","text":"Estudio de enfermedad hemolítica del recién nacido.","guid":"fDGHwRh_PpJltHLNbBaDXQ","children":[]},{"id":"111","parent":"108","text":"No es necesaria para el diagnóstico de AHAI, pero complementa estudio.","guid":"O2529QbFnoIU0R_bL7_f4w","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"112","parent":"104","text":"Crioglobulinas:","guid":"SH-ECyIpu_9YnoR2QJL-8A","children":[{"id":"113","parent":"112","text":"Inmunoglobulinas que precipitan a bajas temperaturas (<37°C).","guid":"FFG4tz3xvygWOzHSZjajEg","children":[]},{"id":"114","parent":"112","text":"Asociadas a trastornos linfoproliferativos e infecciones virales crónicas.","guid":"Ez1-lnhi9HYri7zRbciymQ","children":[]},{"id":"115","parent":"112","text":"Pueden generar síntomas por hiperviscosidad y vasculitis.","guid":"P3bxBji_Oa1zHNmLOVbFaw","children":[]},{"id":"116","parent":"112","text":"Su presencia orienta a AHAI secundaria.\\NRequiere mayor estudio.","guid":"Luy_SWs5Cggs5oW8EVQZ9A","children":[]}]},{"id":"117","parent":"104","text":"Crioaglutininas:","guid":"dn4JGQxh4L5L4_hqQzVKqQ","children":[{"id":"118","parent":"117","text":"Anticuerpos (usualmente IgM) que aglutinan eritrocitos a bajas temperaturas (<30°C).","guid":"P9MkBABfBWxwEe8EO13F6A","children":[]},{"id":"119","parent":"117","text":"Títulos >1:64 a 4°C son significativos y sugieren enfermedad por aglutininas frías (EAF). (4)","guid":"PQiQwjprhd1MwO8wOToYgw","children":[]},{"id":"120","parent":"117","text":"Especificidad anti-I se asocia a EAF primaria,\\Nanti-i a EAF secundaria.","guid":"UurEbzJ1Yf0lUJvgDlk7ZA","children":[]},{"id":"121","parent":"117","text":"Permiten diagnóstico y clasificación de EAF. Monitorización de respuesta a tratamiento.","guid":"OTsAfzohu7w-GRtHTYy5Ng","children":[]}]},{"id":"122","parent":"104","text":"- Estudio de médula ósea","guid":"nvc9d097TkTbo5h8sxmWdw","children":[]}]},{"id":"123","parent":"90","text":"Referencias:","guid":"a7D510T9pH5PY30_A79Mng","children":[{"id":"124","parent":"123","text":"(1) Hill QA, et al. Blood Adv. 2019;3(12):1897-1906.","guid":"TLdBkF9PGRl5GawUDC4ylg","children":[]},{"id":"125","parent":"123","text":"(2) Jäger U, et al. Blood Rev. 2020;41:100648.","guid":"GA5Sxmw2hZ9FhPgBRvsSEA","children":[]},{"id":"126","parent":"123","text":"(3) Brugnara C, Berentsen S. UpToDate. 2023.","guid":"V2-PqHJrfb1YTywEF0KzrA","children":[]},{"id":"127","parent":"123","text":"(4) Berentsen S. Semin Hematol. 2018;55(3):141-149.","guid":"csqDKkhhGwhSoHmUL9MT7A","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"128","parent":"0","text":"Diagnóstico","guid":"","children":[{"id":"129","parent":"128","text":"- Diagnóstico clínico + laboratorio","guid":"CUQGPbg1wKQI-zXAUDUIJA","children":[{"id":"130","parent":"129","text":"Anemia, reticulocitosis, PCD (+), ↑ bilirrubina indirecta, ↑ LDH.","guid":"LCTvVip5HAsu72V7Nbuhaw","children":[]}]},{"id":"131","parent":"128","text":"- Clasificar según PCD\\Nmonoespecífica en","guid":"7xC2xnErhXv0Mfd8qrFSQA","children":[{"id":"132","parent":"131","text":"- AHAI por Ac calientes","guid":"hj-kOgxZ-gxbjXtXIOUHOw","children":[{"id":"133","parent":"132","text":"IgG +/- C3d (+). 70-80% casos.","guid":"39GdDc4KHPV8GB3qYcPKPA","children":[]}]},{"id":"134","parent":"131","text":"- AHAI por Ac\\Nfríos (EAF)","guid":"2jm7gALaaXPfjpQtRetMPA","children":[{"id":"135","parent":"134","text":"C3d (+). Títulos crioglutininas >1:64. 15-25%.","guid":"lleYs_SDc9OjFXPWJNV2-g","children":[]}]},{"id":"136","parent":"131","text":"- AHAI mixta","guid":"KBCbs3mlf_XihrpnF6GIKQ","children":[{"id":"137","parent":"136","text":"IgG + C3d (+). <10%. Peor pronóstico.","guid":"qYk6kZ9qfGbLp0BbfPhE7w","children":[]},{"id":"138","parent":"136","text":"- Descartar AHAI secundaria (neoplasia, infección, autoinmunidad). (1,3,4)","guid":"DlB-LaLnujStbdc4r3HR1A","children":[]}]}]}]},{"id":"139","parent":"0","text":"Diagnósticos\\Ndiferenciales","guid":"CNTFzlB7tA2HzbdWNQQo6w","children":[{"id":"140","parent":"139","text":"- Anemia hemolítica no inmune","guid":"lo0msUxFnlTtoGbaPhmt9A","children":[]},{"id":"141","parent":"139","text":"- Hereditarias","guid":"NTdiRxifUd1z0Vhg7bsSBw","children":[{"id":"142","parent":"141","text":"Esferocitosis hereditaria, déficit G6PDH, talasemias.","guid":"Zx7xhFX86XtXhpLdxCYx0w","children":[]}]},{"id":"143","parent":"139","text":"- Adquiridas","guid":"glfFYlCr83nVTqdFjXUsyg","children":[{"id":"144","parent":"143","text":"HPN, PTT, CID, síndrome urémico-hemolítico (SHU),\\Nválvulas cardíacas, infecciones (malaria, babesiosis).","guid":"I5HiT9jWO4uxra9DMF43Qg","children":[]}]},{"id":"145","parent":"139","text":"- Anemia no hemolítica","guid":"vqZi08exqLMXGLaeqZndjw","children":[{"id":"146","parent":"145","text":"Ferropenia, infiltración medular, aplasia medular.","guid":"hdNryJf_BtliJOWHvKNfMQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"147","parent":"139","text":"- Otras causas de hiperbilirrubinemia. (1,3)","guid":"AIeXpAkBb3mquQJyCeQ_Hw","children":[]}]},{"id":"148","parent":"0","text":"Tratamiento","guid":"","children":[{"id":"149","parent":"148","text":"- Objetivo","guid":"xmEtyvL_p6FAMY-IQ6LtuQ","children":[{"id":"150","parent":"149","text":"Reducir destrucción eritrocitos, controlar anemia, minimizar exposición a corticoides.","guid":"c-ub2OgdI2S1UnRFKbzRWw","children":[]}]},{"id":"151","parent":"148","text":"- No farmacológico","guid":"EKyz6Q9_HfeMUKWHepP4YA","children":[{"id":"152","parent":"151","text":"Evitar exposición a frío en AHAI por Ac fríos.\\NMantener temp. >37°C durante procedimientos.","guid":"ukRFXqudPdcndtDZeDeHyQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"153","parent":"148","text":"- 1era línea","guid":"_CsKe2Yxy5n7hZoMn8j2dQ","children":[{"id":"154","parent":"153","text":"- AHAI por Ac calientes","guid":"ExPc8jhOR-ZJHWsTi1TBQQ","children":[{"id":"155","parent":"154","text":"Prednisona 1 mg/kg/d. 70-80% respuesta.","guid":"Dl8EQhYOFR8iL-yNss1sNQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"156","parent":"153","text":"- AHAI por Ac fríos","guid":"05coDYQW8S1ZzzHa6aNqZg","children":[{"id":"157","parent":"156","text":"Rituximab 375 mg/m2 semanal x4. 50-60% respuesta.","guid":"tzBhtOYbgw5tBmclzc1heg","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"158","parent":"148","text":"- 2da línea (refractarios/intolerantes a\\N1era línea)","guid":"OLbnifdo250lXw1Szh9ulg","children":[{"id":"159","parent":"158","text":"- AHAI por Ac calientes","guid":"ue1g48zDZV5lDlVn7fDBcA","children":[{"id":"160","parent":"159","text":"Rituximab, esplenectomía.","guid":"1ApVS5r2QY_pAzsTZ2Qaiw","children":[]}]},{"id":"161","parent":"158","text":"- AHAI por Ac fríos","guid":"rVnJvvGJrm4IlZ8Y-FE1VQ","children":[{"id":"162","parent":"161","text":"Agentes alquilantes (ciclofosfamida, clorambucil).","guid":"H-CLKBHDIAXWsIutnjwMMA","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"163","parent":"148","text":"- 3era línea","guid":"SCCBSZ-DNeNnNkwKlb6qhg","children":[{"id":"164","parent":"163","text":"Micofenolato, azatioprina, ciclosporina,\\Ndanazol, alemtuzumab, bortezomib.","guid":"ili5pTnUqeniDrqH00C2pA","children":[]}]},{"id":"165","parent":"148","text":"- Emergencia","guid":"V-iTpinYA8cEfCzr23GN0Q","children":[{"id":"166","parent":"165","text":"Metilprednisolona IV 250-1000 mg/d x3d. IgIV 1 g/kg x1-2 dosis. Recambios plasmáticos. (1,3,4)","guid":"OxoDLDuNaAb4bwqLEOfqtg","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"167","parent":"0","text":"Seguimiento","guid":"2zf8vXbt9dkLEPiHzlglmg","children":[{"id":"168","parent":"167","text":"- Control periódico con hemograma, reticulocitos, bilirrubina, LDH hasta estabilización.","guid":"m4mcmWXzOeaKutK-RKkrSQ","children":[]},{"id":"169","parent":"167","text":"- Monitorizar efectos adversos de tratamiento inmunosupresor (infección, DMO, glicemia).","guid":"XgYpPJd78A3afPtccqOA5w","children":[]},{"id":"170","parent":"167","text":"- Considerar profilaxis para P. jirovecii e infecciones virales con rituximab.","guid":"phFsVJ_CWDGze-Swvh5QhQ","children":[]},{"id":"171","parent":"167","text":"- Pronóstico","guid":"khGGYbygktODbu9sByb4rw","children":[{"id":"172","parent":"171","text":"Variable según severidad. En estudios 70-80% RC, 50% recaen dentro de 1-2 años. (1)","guid":"sPPhPrZaTJxkU2L8Dawtlw","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"173","parent":"0","text":"Prevención","guid":"","children":[{"id":"174","parent":"173","text":"- Evitar exposición a frío en pacientes con AHAI por Ac fríos.","guid":"ow-RPZPQddoHzLmOyl7VUA","children":[]},{"id":"175","parent":"173","text":"- Control adecuado de enfermedades autoinmunes de base.","guid":"qMzPVIPr_VhsLdZ3yf1GmA","children":[]}]},{"id":"176","parent":"0","text":"Tamizaje","guid":"","children":[{"id":"177","parent":"176","text":"- No recomendado en población general asintomática.","guid":"ejzzjvZutYfRze8xjUyY4A","children":[]},{"id":"178","parent":"176","text":"- Considerar estudio con PCD en pacientes con anemia de causa no clara o otra autoinmunidad.","guid":"gD4X8jasqP117Tz0UqCviw","children":[]}]},{"id":"179","parent":"0","text":"Aspectos geriátricos","guid":"","children":[{"id":"180","parent":"179","text":"- Presentación clínica inespecífica, confundible con otros síndromes geriátricos.","guid":"ODij2ysGLwXX9YuYkFp6Vg","children":[]},{"id":"181","parent":"179","text":"- Mayor riesgo de efectos adversos a inmunosupresión.","guid":"kbmcaAUT4Snn3_tpDfxQOw","children":[]},{"id":"182","parent":"179","text":"- Metas de tratamiento enfocadas en calidad de vida. Menor umbral para transfusión.","guid":"HsnSPgs6dYtkZwKcHdNkIA","children":[]}]},{"id":"183","parent":"0","text":"Referencias","guid":"","children":[{"id":"184","parent":"183","text":"(1) Jäger U, et al. Blood Rev. 2020;41:100648.","guid":"XoSWGYU2qrVBvdy-mGKzVQ","children":[]},{"id":"185","parent":"183","text":"(2) Hill QA, et al. Blood Adv. 2019;3(12):1897-1906.","guid":"_hm40vVcbn6KimbuTTKDew","children":[]},{"id":"186","parent":"183","text":"(3) Barcellini W, Fattizzo B. Blood. 2021;137(10):1283-1294.","guid":"I96cwtKIarouIVl-vCp-Pw","children":[]},{"id":"187","parent":"183","text":"(4) Berentsen S. Semin Hematol. 2018;55(3):141-149.","guid":"0SjY8v-FCd-l9bZ-WJZeBg","children":[]},{"id":"188","parent":"183","text":"(5) Brodsky RA. N Engl J Med. 2019;381(7):647-654.","guid":"FrSXFZxZogJeVJKi7FYppQ","children":[]},{"id":"189","parent":"183","text":"(6) Saha M, et al. Autoimmun Rev. 2021;20(4):102774.","guid":"eh7d5nmKlEOJ7zbID4fIrA","children":[]},{"id":"190","parent":"183","text":"(7) Kalfa TA. Hematology Am Soc Hematol Educ Program. 2016;2016(1):690-697.","guid":"3tuCanyWqCM-b7kyAOOVIQ","children":[]},{"id":"191","parent":"183","text":"(8) Barcellini W, et al. Blood. 2014;124(22):3228-37.","guid":"6WBL9ESQ13E6RpCm5QoXtQ","children":[]},{"id":"192","parent":"183","text":"(9) Velásquez MP, et al. Rev Med Chil. 2018;146(9):1043-1050.","guid":"-EMnVqJIyZvO9wlXStv2nw","children":[]},{"id":"193","parent":"183","text":"(10) Hansen DL, et al. Clin Epidemiol. 2020; 12:497-510.","guid":"J8vc0Fc3AX3pqCxwILXfNQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"194","parent":"0","text":"Abreviaturas","guid":"BLKteCZEckFB0DNxZ2K_AA","children":[{"id":"195","parent":"194","text":"AHAI: Anemia hemolítica autoinmune","guid":"VWQOYc2qaz9uafUi8JQJqQ","children":[]},{"id":"196","parent":"194","text":"ADCC: Citotoxicidad celular dependiente de anticuerpos","guid":"SgedCX3J8TWoZHLWSjkWFw","children":[]},{"id":"197","parent":"194","text":"CHCM: Concentración de hemoglobina corpuscular media","guid":"HY0_4kD8CC6vRBFOeFNz6w","children":[]},{"id":"198","parent":"194","text":"CID: Coagulación intravascular diseminada","guid":"R42s67ng-bs9fy1p0RhETQ","children":[]},{"id":"199","parent":"194","text":"DMO: Densidad mineral ósea","guid":"V-bzbsOxl6yjGu96cmotAQ","children":[]},{"id":"200","parent":"194","text":"EAF: Enfermedad por aglutininas frías","guid":"JclfuNgnTme2nqg8kMfdxA","children":[]},{"id":"201","parent":"194","text":"G6PDH: Glucosa-6-fosfato deshidrogenasa","guid":"Xcvw_0KWqA3KTtAF9HbtiQ","children":[]},{"id":"202","parent":"194","text":"HPN: Hemoglobinuria paroxística nocturna","guid":"nPVbbAUxVZRJofw1ehifmA","children":[]},{"id":"203","parent":"194","text":"IgIV: Inmunoglobulina intravenosa","guid":"ujP-pWzoEh5StapkCFoJiA","children":[]},{"id":"204","parent":"194","text":"LDH: Lactato deshidrogenasa","guid":"OssL5ggimGHP6Qz__xb1wA","children":[]},{"id":"205","parent":"194","text":"LLC: Leucemia linfocítica crónica","guid":"Rsb0ASuHO7oniubKRj3eMQ","children":[]},{"id":"206","parent":"194","text":"LES: Lupus eritematoso sistémico","guid":"4XfeZWB3G6dMEuUfmZjTeg","children":[]},{"id":"207","parent":"194","text":"PCD: Prueba de Coombs directa","guid":"sqhGR7rfS3oxgll0DG8Aeg","children":[]},{"id":"208","parent":"194","text":"PTT: Púrpura trombótica trombocitopénica","guid":"MYty1S8kcTIDcDKmK2zFzw","children":[]},{"id":"209","parent":"194","text":"SHU: Síndrome hemolítico urémico","guid":"zaDmseGCBYtcFovXasU_Sw","children":[]}]},{"id":"210","parent":"0","text":"Enfermedad por\\NAglutininas Frías (EAF)","guid":"Yvg-N2rfD7UTmvvLIXspXQ","children":[{"id":"211","parent":"210","text":"AHAI causada por anticuerpos que aglutinan los eritrocitos a bajas temperaturas,\\Ntípicamente IgM. Se clasifica en primaria (idiopática) y secundaria según su etiología.","guid":"Jq7pEiUc-ydEi7anHxaoQg","children":[]},{"id":"212","parent":"210","text":"EAF Primaria:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"213","parent":"212","text":"También conocida como Hemolisina Fría Idiopática o Hemolisina Fría Esencial.","guid":"SRp7wHcCckdOHVbjHyXyvw","children":[]},{"id":"214","parent":"212","text":"Trastorno linfoproliferativo de células B clonales que producen crioglutininas (IgM monoclonal). (1)","guid":"BOKTLydWnW1WAG5hFGShdw","children":[]},{"id":"215","parent":"212","text":"Predomina en adultos mayores (media de edad 70-80 años).","guid":"FXa0xX9BMRMmUEk1KriyWA","children":[]},{"id":"216","parent":"212","text":"Crioglutininas con especificidad anti-I en la mayoría de los casos.","guid":"PwX1IAO6uXBSS8kJQ7iimA","children":[]},{"id":"217","parent":"212","text":"No se asocia a otra enfermedad subyacente.","guid":"Kf8rsRQb_HsrG2GZDPdp6Q","children":[]},{"id":"218","parent":"212","text":"Curso crónico con exacerbaciones en invierno.","guid":"fvsMMD62XWQucpNGClj1Jg","children":[]},{"id":"219","parent":"212","text":"Tratamiento dirigido a linfoproliferación de células B (Rituximab, quimioterapia). (2)","guid":"EXPsQz8XwD0kLxiVOCLVVQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"220","parent":"210","text":"EAF Secundaria:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"221","parent":"220","text":"Ocurre en el contexto de otra enfermedad o condición predisponente.","guid":"ZDS7ZGi6zzxXOX2YLU83JA","children":[]},{"id":"222","parent":"220","text":"Causas:","guid":"X71BhCVW1HtMdSnjZJ_Usw","children":[{"id":"223","parent":"222","text":"Infecciones: Mycoplasma pneumoniae, Virus Epstein Barr (VEB), Citomegalovirus (CMV), VIH.","guid":"TK1x6CJ1mER5BHYqYiQmrQ","children":[]},{"id":"224","parent":"222","text":"Enfermedades autoinmunes: Lupus Eritematoso Sistémico (LES), Artritis Reumatoide (AR).","guid":"IbbJVx9Uv2AM3NkGYLy-dw","children":[]},{"id":"225","parent":"222","text":"Neoplasias: Linfoma, Leucemia Linfocítica Crónica (LLC), Macroglobulinemia de Waldenstrom.","guid":"Iw940F8oog8kdWEPTQ6kgQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"226","parent":"220","text":"Crioglutininas pueden tener especificidad anti-i (infecciones) o anti-I (neoplasias, autoinmunidad). (3)","guid":"c0Seik-QwqhaBg5qcj-qug","children":[]},{"id":"227","parent":"220","text":"Curso variable según enfermedad de base. Puede ser agudo y autolimitado (infecciones) o crónico.","guid":"DkcgDQh4obB8mJ_hH7sMUA","children":[]},{"id":"228","parent":"220","text":"Manejo enfocado en tratamiento de condición subyacente. Puede requerir terapia específica para crioglutininas en casos severos.","guid":"R5Bh7SDHuHZX3eGmK8UdUQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"229","parent":"210","text":"Diferencias Pronósticas\\Ny de Manejo:","guid":"CYKHsy8XXz5ZFFR1aT_JNw","children":[{"id":"230","parent":"229","text":"EAF primaria tiene mejor pronóstico que secundarias a neoplasias.","guid":"VG4zuSWJflhN353qIRulog","children":[]},{"id":"231","parent":"229","text":"EAF secundaria a infecciones suele ser autolimitada y de buen pronóstico.","guid":"R_8WnEbkFBUDP8xPabXf8w","children":[]},{"id":"232","parent":"229","text":"EAF primaria y secundarias crónicas pueden requerir tratamiento indefinido.","guid":"ZjjTdRAcpVVKcp5qCUhMRQ","children":[]},{"id":"233","parent":"229","text":"En EAF secundaria es fundamental el manejo de la condición de base.","guid":"b0VHZW7n_3pWVvDGYonl7w","children":[]}]},{"id":"234","parent":"210","text":"Referencias:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"235","parent":"234","text":"(1) Berentsen S. Hematology Am Soc Hematol Educ Program. 2016;2016(1):690-697.","guid":"ONWg4VFiMItseu6AAGYCzw","children":[]},{"id":"236","parent":"234","text":"(2) Berentsen S, et al. Blood. 2020;136(4):480-488.","guid":"cinpAURY0CYsKyAge6xwtA","children":[]},{"id":"237","parent":"234","text":"(3) Swiecicki PL, et al. Blood. 2013;122(23):3759-3766.","guid":"c3AvZAU_dJZk7DnrR95jHQ","children":[]}]}]}]},"node_count":237,"relations":[],"cross_references":[],"specialty":"Hematología","folder":"Entidades clínicas/Hematología","filename":"Anemia Hemolítica Autoinmune-2024","id":"map_1049","resolved_references":[],"title_raw":"Anemia Hemolítica Autoinmune-2024"}